name: Wumpscut
description: '''Wumpscut''' (stylised as ''':wumpscut:''' or simply ''':w:''') is a [[Gothic rock|gothic]]-influenced [[electro-industrial]] music project from Germany. It was founded in May 1991 by [[Bavaria]]n disc jockey Rudolf "Rudy" Ratzinger (born 1966). Through 2016, Rudy Ratzinger released seventeen studio albums plus a number of compilations: demos, compilation tracks, and remixes from deleted singles and EPs.
